title: Game of Thrones
plot: In the mythical continent of Westeros, several powerful families fight for control of the Seven Kingdoms. As conflict erupts in the kingdoms of men, an ancient enemy rises once again to threaten them all. Meanwhile, the last heirs of a recently usurped dynasty plot to take back their homeland from across the Narrow Sea.
awards: Top Rated TV #12 | Won 1 Golden Globe. Another 377 wins & 616 nominations.
stars: Emilia Clarke, Peter Dinklage, Kit Harington, Lena Headey
companies: Home Box Office (HBO), Television 360, Grok! Studio

similars.title: Breaking Bad
similars.plot: A high school chemistry teacher diagnosed with inoperable lung cancer turns to manufacturing and selling methamphetamine in order to secure his family's future.
similars.stars: Bryan Cranston, Aaron Paul, Anna Gunn

similars.title: Stranger Things
similars.plot: When a young boy disappears, his mother, a police chief and his friends must confront terrifying supernatural forces in order to get him back.
similars.stars: Millie Bobby Brown, Finn Wolfhard, Winona Ryder

similars.title: Chernobyl
similars.plot: In April 1986, an explosion at the Chernobyl nuclear power plant in the Union of Soviet Socialist Republics becomes one of the world's worst man-made catastrophes.
similars.stars: Jessie Buckley, Jared Harris, Stellan Skarsgård

similars.title: Peaky Blinders
similars.plot: A gangster family epic set in 1900s England, centering on a gang who sew razor blades in the peaks of their caps, and their fierce boss Tommy Shelby.
similars.stars: Cillian Murphy, Paul Anderson, Helen McCrory

similars.title: Vikings
similars.plot: Vikings transports us to the brutal and mysterious world of Ragnar Lothbrok, a Viking warrior and farmer who yearns to explore - and raid - the distant shores across the ocean.
similars.stars: Katheryn Winnick, Gustaf Skarsgård, Alexander Ludwig

similars.title: Friends

similars.stars: Jennifer Aniston, Courteney Cox, Lisa Kudrow

similars.plot: A modern update finds the famous sleuth and his doctor partner solving crime in 21st century London.
similars.stars: Benedict Cumberbatch, Martin Freeman, Una Stubbs

similars.plot: Sheriff Deputy Rick Grimes wakes up from a coma to learn the world is in ruins and must lead a group of survivors to stay alive.

similars.plot: An unusual group of robbers attempt to carry out the most perfect robbery in Spanish history - stealing 2.4 billion euros from the Royal Mint of Spain.

similars.title: The Sopranos
similars.plot: New Jersey mob boss Tony Soprano deals with personal and professional issues in his home and business life that affect his mental state, leading him to seek professional psychiatric counseling.
